    <primary sortas="a-qrcodegencpp">QR-Code-generator</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to QR-Code-generator</title>

    <para>
      The QR-Code-generator package provides a QR code generator.
    </para>

    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Download (HTTP): <ulink url="&qrcodegencpp-download-http;"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Additional Downloads</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist spacing="compact">
      <listitem>
        <para>
          Required CMake files:
          <ulink url="https://github.com/EasyCoding/qrcodegen-cmake/archive/v&qrcodegencpp-version;-cmake3/qrcodegen-cmake-&qrcodegencpp-version;-cmake3.tar.gz"/>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">QR-Code-generator Dependencies</bridgehead>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Required</bridgehead>
    <para role="required">
      <ulink url="&blfs-svn;/general/cmake.html">CMake</ulink>
    </para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of QR-Code-generator</title>

    <para>
      First unpack the CMake files:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>tar -xf ../qrcodegen-cmake-&qrcodegencpp-version;-cmake3.tar.gz &amp;&amp;
cp -vR qrcodegen-cmake-&qrcodegencpp-version;-cmake3/{cmake,CMakeLists.txt} . &amp;&amp;
rm -rf qrcodegen-cmake-&qrcodegencpp-version;-cmake3</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install <application>QR-Code-generator</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

cmake -D CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr   \
      -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release    \
      -D CMAKE_SKIP_INSTALL_RPATH=ON \
      -D BUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON        \
      -G Ninja .. &amp;&amp;

ninja</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the &root; user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>
  
  <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Command Explanations</title>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
      href="../../xincludes/cmake-skip-install-rpath.xml"/>

    <para>
      <parameter>-D BUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON</parameter>: This ensures shared
      libraries are built.
    </para>

